The paper discusses a method for training neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning. Specifically, it focuses on deep learning, which is a subfield of machine learning that deals with neural networks with multiple layers. The paper also mentions experiments with image datasets, indicating a focus on computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision). Other possible categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
